WEBVTT

00:03.038 --> 00:05.830
Sheldon Cooper's
descent into madness...

00:05.846 --> 00:09.315
day two.

00:09.317 --> 00:10.850
It's 2:25 a.m.,

00:10.852 --> 00:14.787
and I feel the urge to urinate.

00:14.789 --> 00:18.090
My normal urination time
is 7:10 a.m.,

00:18.092 --> 00:21.027
but here I am,
in the middle of the night,

00:21.029 --> 00:23.195
struggling to keep my mind sharp

00:23.197 --> 00:26.999
and my pajamas dry.

00:27.001 --> 00:28.301
It's only a matter of time

00:28.303 --> 00:32.872
before my tenuous grasp
on reality fades.

00:32.874 --> 00:36.842
I suppose I should pee while
I still know what a toilet is.

